'''近燈籠海膽'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|'''''Plesiolampas'''''}}）是一[[屬|屬]]已[[滅絕|滅絕]]的[[海膽|海膽]]，生存在[[始新世|始新世]]的[[非洲|非洲]]及[[亞洲|亞洲]]。牠們的[[介殼|介殼]]為圓圓的[[五邊形|五邊形]]，從側面看為矮[[錐體|錐體]]狀。[[橢圓形|橢圓形]]的[[口|口]]位於下部中心的深處，[[肛門|肛門]]位於後部邊緣。五條[[花瓣|花瓣]]狀步帶很長，並長有長孔。介殼的上部表面均勻地覆蓋著細小的刺瘤。蛇頸海膽生活在[[海|海]]底的沙中，將自己埋在沙質沉積裡覓食。<ref>{{cite book | title=自然珍藏系列──化石圖鑑 | location = [[台灣|台灣]][[新北市|新北市]] | publisher=[[貓頭鷹出版社|貓頭鷹出版社]] | author= Cyril Walker | author2= Davod Ward | authorlink=Cyril Walker (palaeontologist) | authorlink2=David Ward (palaeontologist) | series=自然珍藏系列 | year=2002 | page=181 | date = 2002-02 | language = zh-hant}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | title=Fossils | url=https://archive.org/details/fossils0000walk_e1r0 | publisher=[[Dorling_Kindersley|Dorling Kindersley]] | author=Walker, Cyril | last2=Ward | first2=David | authorlink=Cyril Walker (palaeontologist) | authorlink2=David Ward (palaeontologist) | series=Smithsonian Handbooks | year=2002 | page=[https://archive.org/details/fossils0000walk_e1r0/page/181 181] | isbn=0789489848 | edition=revised, illustrated}}</ref>

